# Cursor AI Rules for nicegui-template

**Read these files before working:**

1. [README.md](../README.md) - Project overview and setup
2. [AGENT.md](../AGENT.md) - AI agent guidelines
3. [CONTRIBUTING.md](../CONTRIBUTING.md) - Coding standards and workflow

## Quick Reference

- This is a **Copier template project** - work with Jinja2 templating
- Use single quotes in Python
- 120 character line length
- Think from first principles
- Keep templates generic and universal
- Test all option combinations
- Update README.md when adding copier.yml questions
